Manage a local instance of Apache Kafka.

Usage:
  confluent local kafka [command]

Available Commands:
  broker      Manage local Kafka brokers.
  cluster     Manage the local Kafka cluster.
  start       Start a local Apache Kafka instance.
  stop        Stop the local Apache Kafka service.
  topic       Run Kafka topic related commands.

Global Flags:
  -h, --help            Show help for this command.
      --unsafe-trace    Equivalent to -vvvv, but also log HTTP requests and responses which might contain plaintext secrets.
  -v, --verbose count   Increase verbosity (-v for warn, -vv for info, -vvv for debug, -vvvv for trace).

Use "confluent local kafka [command] --help" for more information about a command.
